{"tid":1810819,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[社會話題作品]麥路人討論區","createTime":"2020-01-04T07:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T03:48:43.000Z","uid":206762,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eabd22ef9498079e5b44ec1a7ac6da6d958f5f46","tid":1810819,"uid":206762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yn70XAu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYn70XAu.jpg&h=e7b78c70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預告片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nlh16FWBh7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fnlh16FWBh7U&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDsljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=5f03be15\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nlh16FWBh7U</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劇情：幾個坎坷故事，道盡繁華城市背後的悲情世界&hellip;&hellip; 假如，我們相信，希望能燃點生命；信念能改寫人生，或許，是我們不知道，希望和信念，往往會瓦解於貧窮&hellip;&hellip; 阿博(郭富城 飾)曾是金融才俊，一次失誤他挪用公款，結果成了階下囚。阿博入獄後回歸社會，他愧疚不想回家，更自暴自棄，從此成了無家者，活在眾多比他更無明天的人當中，找回些安全感。十年前與阿珍 (楊千嬅 飾) 一面之緣，因與陳博惺惺相惜而漸漸走近，希望一天令他重新能振作&hellip;&hellip; 同是無家者的媽媽(劉雅瑟 飾) 帶著囡囡和悲涼的過去輾轉到港成了麥難民。深仔(顧定軒 飾) 一直宅在家中，沉迷打機，拒絕踏足社會。一次與嫂嫂爭執令他與阿哥大打出手後，最終離家出走。他們與等伯(萬梓良 飾)、口水祥(張達明 飾)和一眾開始了一段交淺情深的故事&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n演員：郭富城、楊千嬅、萬梓良、張達明、鮑起靜、顧定軒、劉雅瑟、岑日珈、勞浩羽及黃悅珈<br />\n導演：黃慶勳<br />\n監制：鄭保瑞<br />\n上映日期：2020年4月30日(資料係咁寫 唔知會唔會再轉)<br />\n<br />\n我相信呢套都會有人話邊個邊個做 不了<br />\n但呢套戲主要都係講緊社會低下階層人仕既苦況 絕對值得大家入場支持 <br />\n樓主自己就未睇 但我相信銀河映像出身既兩個幕後搞既電影 應該都唔差 所以大家睇唔睇就自己衡量 希望大家多多支持本土話題之作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家已經睇左想討論套戲 劇透既地方麻煩轉色轉細字 保障下未睇既觀眾(包括樓主)"},{"pid":"afef5095c7f565a227594273f2a3f1f1d69c729f","tid":1810819,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:14:24.000Z","msg":"顧定軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e91f3598bcdad834545f6dd21b8c7b52e4bd744","tid":1810819,"uid":122110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:22:25.000Z","msg":"本土電影值得支持啦，而家根本冇戲係完全100%黃色娛樂圈，連哩啲都罷睇，港產電影真係收得皮，下一代淨係睇支國紅海行動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acaba4115bb8bec882888ed06a2d9f067b784253","tid":1810819,"uid":206762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"好想快啲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6fd593af8369f5eae06a594fc50af5b0a004bc","tid":1810819,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f689d25d6d81d79821a893f4938e253ed997696","tid":1810819,"uid":206762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:11:31.000Z","msg":"希望大家係上映期間會多多留意"},{"pid":"a75aab43ae5f724c0e937253c685746a67c261fa","tid":1810819,"uid":246962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"睇咗，媽媽劉雅瑟做得好好，好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外樓主唔好意思，借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n呼喚 冇咩嘢好做 師兄，個港產片post爆咗啦，請開part 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bba177f78d97f80e09cc8cab760dca72651434","tid":1810819,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a75aab43ae5f724c0e937253c685746a67c261fa","tid":1810819,"uid":246962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"睇咗，媽媽劉雅瑟做得好好，好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外樓主唔好意思，借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n呼喚 冇咩嘢好做 師兄，個港產片post爆咗啦，請開part 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:51:41.000